ZH: 我们都有自己的理想。
EN: We all have our own ideals.

ZH: 在我的理想中，我希望成为一名作家。
EN: In my ideal world, I would like to become a writer.

ZH: 她理想中的生活是在海边度假。
EN: Her ideal life is to vacation by the seaside.

ZH: 理想中的爱情是永远不变的。
EN: Ideal love is everlasting.

ZH: 理想与现实之间总是存在差距。
EN: There is always a gap between ideals and reality.

ZH: 他一直向往着一个自由自在的理想生活。
EN: He has been yearning for a carefree ideal life.

ZH: 学生们应该不断追求自己的理想。
EN: Students should constantly pursue their ideals.

ZH: 他的理想是建立一家属于自己的企业。
EN: His ideal is to establish his own business.

ZH: 珍惜你的理想，付诸实践。
EN: Cherish your ideals and put them into practice.

ZH: 他一直以来都在努力向着自己的理想前进。
EN: He has been striving towards his ideals all along.

ZH: 在现实的世界中，理想很难实现。
EN: In the real world, ideals are hard to achieve.

ZH: 他的理想是拯救所有受苦的人。
EN: His ideal is to save all suffering people.

ZH: 父母总是鼓励孩子们追求他们的理想。
EN: Parents always encourage their children to pursue their ideals.

ZH: 她的理想是成为一名成功的科学家。
EN: Her ideal is to become a successful scientist.

ZH: 对理想的追求让人们变得更加有活力。
EN: Pursuing ideals makes people more energetic.

ZH: 我们应该为了自己的理想而努力拼搏。
EN: We should strive for our ideals.

ZH: 珍惜当下，实现你的理想。
EN: Cherish the present and realize your ideals.

ZH: 在生活中，理想可以给人以希望。
EN: In life, ideals can give people hope.

ZH: 不要放弃你的理想，坚持下去。
EN: Don't give up on your ideals, keep going.

ZH: 追求理想的过程会让人变得更加坚强。
EN: The process of pursuing ideals will make people stronger.
